The following considerations were used in this document:
1) Resuls are based on centralized distance matrix only, because it generally shows better PVE and doesn’t cheange the results on GWAS.
2) p-values for likelihood ratio test are used for reporting. Other tests are asymptotically equivalent to LRT.
3) The following methods used for p-values correction: bonferroni, holm, hochberg, fdr, BY
